quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  70,19,Mazima omuntu yatondebwa nga wamulugube
  70,20,Nga bwatuukibwako akabi ayitirira okutya
  70,21,Ate bwaba afunye akalungi ayitirira obukodo
  70,22,Okugyako abo abayimirizaawo e sswala
  70,23,Abo nga okusaala kwabwe kwalubeerera
  70,24,Era abo mu by'obugagga byabwe mulimu omugabo ogumanyiddwa
  70,25,Guweebwa abasabi n'abafuna mpola
  70,26,Era bebo abakakasa o kubeerawo kw'olunaku lw'enkomerero
  70,27,Era abo abatya ebibonerezo bya Mukama Katonda waabwe
  70,28,Kubanga mazima ebibonerezo byamukama Katonda sibyakuwonwa
  70,29,Era abo abakuuma obwerere bwabwe
  70,30,"Okugyako ku bakyala babwe oba abazaana abali mu mikono gyabwe, anti bo tebanenyezebwa kwabo"
  70,31,"Omuntu asukka ku abo, abo nno be babuusi bensalo"
  70,32,"Era abantu abalungi abogeddwako waggulu, bebatuukiriza obwesigwa bwabwe nendagaano zaabwe"
  70,33,Era abo abeesimbu mu bujulizi bwabwe
  70,34,Era abo abasaala e sswala zaabwe mu bujjuvu
  70,35,Abo nno balibeera mu jjana nga baweebwa ebitiibwa
  70,36,"Lwaki abakafiiri bajja gyoli nga banguwa \"so nga ate bakulimbisa"
  70,37,Nga bali ku mukono gwo ogwa ddyo ne ku mukono ogwa kkono mu bibinja
  70,38,Buli omu kubo asuubira okuyingira e jjana eyebyengera
  70,39,"Nedda sibwekiri, mazima ffe twabakola nga tubajja mwebyo byebamanyi"
  70,40,"Ndayira Katonda nannyini buvanjuba nobugwanjuba, mazima ffe tusobolera ddala"
  70,41,Okubawanyisaamu abalungi ababasinga era tetuli ffe baakulemesebwa
  70,42,"Ggwe baveeko babeere mu bukafiiri bwabwe nga bwebazannya okutuusa lwebalisisinkana olunaku lwabwe, olwo lwebalaganyisibwa"
  70,43,Olunaku lwebalifuluma mu ntaana zaabwe nga baduma nga balinga abagenda eri ebendera ebatereddwawo
  70,44,"Amaaso gabwe makakkamu, obuswavu nga bubabuutikidde, olwo lwe lunaku lwe balaganyisibwa"
  71,1,Mazima ffe twatuma Nuhu eri abantu be. Nti tiisa abantubo nga ebibonerezo abiruma ennyo tebinabajjira
  71,2,Naabagamba nti mazima nze ndi mutiisa omunnyonnyozi
  71,3,Nti musinze Katonda era mu mutye nange mungondere
  71,4,Olwo nno ajja kubasonyiwa ebyonoono byammwe (bye mwakola nga temunnaba kukkiriza mubaka era alyoke abawonye okuzikirira n'ebibonerezo ebibamalawo olumu). Abalindirize abatuuse ku ntuuko ze yabagerera. Mazima entuuko za Katonda bweziba zituuse tezirindirizibwa singa muba mumanyi
  71,5,"Awamu nekyo tebakkiriza\", Nuhu naagamba nti ayi Katonda wange nkowodde abantu bange ekiro n'emisana"
  71,6,Wabula okukowoola kwange tekubongedde okugyako okunnesamba
  71,7,"Mazima buli lwembadde mbakowoola badde eri okusonyiwa kwo bassa ennwe zaabwe mu matu gaabwe, ne beebikka engoye zaabwe, ne bakalambira era ne beekuluntaza olw'ekuluntaza"
  71,8,Ate era mazima mbakowodde mulwatu
  71,9,Era njogedde nabo mu lujjudde nga bwenjogedde nabo kinnomu
  71,10,Nembagamba nti mwegayirire Katonda wa mmwe anti mazima yye bulijjo musonyiyi
  71,11,Olwonno ajja kubatonnyeseza enkuba ey'omuddiringanwa
  71,12,Era abawe mu bungi emmaali n'abaana abawe n'amasamba abateeremu n'emigga
  71,13,Naye lwaki Katonda temumuwa kitiibwa
  71,14,Sso nga yabatonda ngabayisa mumitendera egyenjawulo
  71,15,Abaffe temulaba engeri Katondawo gyeyakolamu eggulu omusanvu nga myaliiro
  71,16,Nassaamu omwezi nga kitangaala nga bweyassamu enjuba nga eyaka
  71,17,Katonda yabatandika ng'abajja muttaka nemujja nga mukula nga ebimera bwe bikula
  71,18,Oluvanyuma abazza mu ttaka nga era bwagenda okubazuukiza alibagyemu bulambalamba (nga temuyise mu mitendera nga ebimera)
  71,19,Era Katonda yabateerawo ensi nga esoboka okuwangalirwako
  71,20,Mube nga musobola okutambulira muyo nga mukwata amakubo ge muba mwagadde
  71,21,"Nuhu kwekugamba nti, ayi mukama wange mazima ddala abantu abo banjemedde nebasalawo okugoberera oyo yenna emmaali ye n'abaana be bebitayongera okugyako okufafaganirwa"
  71,22,Nebakola olukwe sinziggu (bwebagezaako okutta Nuhu)
  71,23,Era nebagamba nti temugeza nemuva ku ba Katonda ba mmwe naddala Wadda ne Suwa'a ne Yagutha ne Yauka ne Nasira
  71,24,Olwekyo baabuza abantu bangi (Nange kyenva nkusaba nti) mukama Katonda abantu abeyisa obubi tobongera okugyako kubula
  71,25,Olwobwonoonyi bwabwe baazikiziribwa nebayingizibwa omuliro baali tebayinza kufuna abataasa yenna
  71,26,"Ye Nuhu kwekugamba nti, ayi Katonda wange toleka kunsi mukafiiri yenna"
  71,27,Anti singa obalekawo bajja kubuza abaddu bo era buli gwebanazaala ajja kuba mwononefu omukafiiri
  71,28,"Ayi Mukama Katonda wange nsonyiwa ne bakadde bange na buli yenna anaayingira mu nju yange kavuna anaaba nga mukkiriza, era nkusaba osonyiwe abakkiriza abasajja n'abakkiriza abakazi, wabula bo abeeyisa obubi tobongera okugyako okuzikirira"